    "Html": "my code to update comes from <a href=\"http://www.scottlogic.co.uk/blog/wpf/2009/01/wpf-datagrid-committing-changes-cell-by-cell/\">http://www.scottlogic.co.uk/blog/wpf/2009/01/wpf-datagrid-committing-changes-cell-by-cell/</a><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\"> Private </span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">RowBeingEdited </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">As</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> DataRowView<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\"><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>Private </p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n</span>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">Sub</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> dgRevenue_CellEditEnding(</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">ByVal</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> sender </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">As</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">Object</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\">, </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">ByVal</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> e </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">As</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> Microsoft.Windows.Controls.DataGridCellEditEndingEventArgs) </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">Handles</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> dgRevenue.CellEditEnding<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px\"><br>\r\n    RowBeingEdited = e.Row.Item<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\"><br>\r\nEnd </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">Sub<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:13px\"><span style=\"font-size:13px\">  <br>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">Private</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">Sub</span><span style=\"font-size:13px\"> dgRevenue_CurrentCellChanged(</span><span style=\"font-size:13px;color:#0000ff\">ByVal</span><span style=\"